            "title": "輝達急插6% 納指曾挫逾1%",
            "description": "<p id=\"date\">2025年11月26日</p>\n<p class=\"info\">\t\n</p>\n    <h1 id=\"article-title\" class=\"sub_ex_article-title\">輝達急插6% 納指曾挫逾1%<br>    \n   \n    </h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/11/26/4256272_64da80f05d61f7ef9104489299e1b388.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/11/26/4256272_64da80f05d61f7ef9104489299e1b388_620.png\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/11/26/4256272_64da80f05d61f7ef9104489299e1b388.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a> / <a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/11/26/4256272_64da80f05d61f7ef9104489299e1b388.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">顯示原圖</a></span>\n<p></p>\n美股連續兩日大幅反彈後未有延續強勁勢頭，道指周二高開34點，升幅曾擴大至最多407點，高見46855點，隨後升幅收窄；標指跌0.67%，以科技股為主的納指回落1.25%。\nMeta據報正洽購Alphabet旗下Google的人工智能（AI）晶片，刺激後者股價上揚2%，AI晶片業龍頭的輝達（Nvidi...\n<p>（節錄）</p>",
